  <h1>Evolution of Wired Technology to Wireless</h1>
  
  <div class="timeline">
    <div class="event">
      <h3>Wired Technology</h3>
      <p>From wired to wireless networks, technology has travelled a remarkable path. The earliest networks' range and mobility were constrained since they were physically wired together. Wireless networks were created as technology advanced, allowing for more mobility and range. Wireless networks are widely used in today's world, from mobile phones to smart homes.</p>
    </div>
